        "product_description": {
            "value": [
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "The ASR Outdoor Gold Snifter Squeeze Bottles are an essential gold recovery prospecting tool for all gold prospectors. This handy bottle is perfect for extracting gold from your gold pans. <br/><br/>Simple to use, just squeeze the bottle and use the suction to grab gold flour and flakes and release them into one of our gold collection glass vials. <br/><br/>Each gold snifter bottle is 5\" tall and holds 4 ounces of liquid, and can be used for countless hobbies and crafts. Make sure to keep some of these around whether you're gold prospecting in the field or doing clean up work in the garage.<br/><br/>Come in packs of 2, 3. 4, 6, 8 or 10 units.",
